help.Music:
**play <song id/exact file name>:**  Play a song
**playNow <id or name>:** Play a song now
**playAll (Shuffle):** Add the entire music library into the queue, Shuffle will shuffle the queue
**del <song id/exact file name/range in format x-y>:** Delete a song OR bath delete.
Ex. del 1, del wah.mp3, del 1-3 (deletes song 1,2,3)

**shuffle:** Shuffles the queue
**QUEue:** List current playing queue
**ListSongs:** List entire song library
**next:** Play next song
**prev:** Play previous song
**loop:** Toggles one-song loop
**stop:** Delete queue and leave
**pause:** Pause/resume playback

**MusicAdd <link/alias/attach a file>:** Download/upload a song to music library.
**killdl:** send CTRL + C to dl binary
**ReScan:** Reload music library

**gui:** Spawn a player GUI
**CloseGui:** Destroy active GUI
